reviewText: Me encant este DVD, la calidad de imagen y sonido es genial. Sin embargo, creo que es algo corto. Es mejor el DVD Acoustic Band.

I'm a big fan of all three of these awesome musicians.  I gave it 3 stars because this video was really short.  Nothing like the older Akoustic Band Alive one.

But, This was no doubt a DVD with phenominal performances.  I just wish it was longer.

They are 3 of the most amazing musicians on the planet.  I do recommend this DVD, but know that it's very short.
